text: Tangchi (汤池镇) could refer to the following towns in China: *Tangchi, Tailai County, in Heilongjiang *Tangchi, Dandong, in Zhenxing District, Dandong, Liaoning *Tangchi, Dashiqiao, in Liaoning *Tangchi, Lujiang County, in Anhui *Tangchi, Shucheng County, in Anhui *Tangchi, Yingcheng County, in Hubei *Tangchi, Yiliang County, in Yunnan
title: Tangchi
